'''protoplasm'''
{{wikipedia}}

# {{cytology}} The entire contents of a cell comprising the [[nucleus]] and the [[cytoplasm]]. It is a semi-fluid, [[transparent]] [[substance]] which is the [[living]] [[matter]] of [[plant]] and [[animal]] [[cell]]s.

